Package: RNewsflow
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Comparing Text Messages Across Time and Media
Version: 1.2.4
Author: Kasper Welbers & Wouter van Atteveldt
Maintainer: Kasper Welbers <kasperwelbers@gmail.com>
